theorem Char.ofNat_toNat {c : char} (h : is_valid_char c.to_nat) : char.of_nat c.to_nat = c :=
  by
  rw [char.of_nat, dif_pos h]
  cases c
  simp [char.to_nat]
#align char.of_nat_to_nat Char.ofNat_toNat
-/
